notes: Bait|Red Pheidole. Video of Atta|Set up Connor for the day working on Cacao 1999 malaise traps (2 in the day). Switching rental vehicles at 3pm. Completely clear, somewhat breezy and ciccadas calling all day. Very hot (>30 C). Traps out and bait down at 9:20am. GigaPan at Bait 6 was problematic (batteries died and the shutter arm fell off). took about 4hrs to finish with a hard re-start. Ticks everywhere. Videos of Atta at Bait 2, Large Camponotus at Bait 5, Crematogaster, Atta and Solenopsis at Bait 3 and Small Camponotus at Bait 4. All up at 2:50pm. Dominant species, Paratrechina and Solenopsis|Waypoint 33||http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xU1xJAwE2Vw|http://www.gigapan.org/gigapans/71622/|http://bit.ly/dQDt90|https://sites.google.com/site/acgantcollectionsfeb2011/|Worker

notes: Pitfall||Set up Connor for the day working on Cacao 1999 malaise traps (2 in the day). Switching rental vehicles at 3pm. Completely clear, somewhat breezy and ciccadas calling all day. Very hot (>30 C). Traps out and bait down at 9:20am. GigaPan at Bait 6 was problematic (batteries died and the shutter arm fell off). took about 4hrs to finish with a hard re-start. Ticks everywhere. Videos of Atta at Bait 2, Large Camponotus at Bait 5, Crematogaster, Atta and Solenopsis at Bait 3 and Small Camponotus at Bait 4. All up at 2:50pm. Dominant species, Paratrechina and Solenopsis|Waypoint 33|||http://www.gigapan.org/gigapans/71622/|http://bit.ly/dQDt90|https://sites.google.com/site/acgantcollectionsfeb2011/|Worker
